    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver\u2019s specimen featuring the legendary S54 inline-six, delivering peak power through six individual throttle bodies. The powertrain is mated to a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual and a factory limited-slip differential. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and subframe reinforcement\u2014essential for long-term chassis rigidity. Suspension remains taut with refreshed bushings, and the high-revving induction note is unmistakable. A mechanically sound example ready for the apex.",
