      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound E92 M3, featuring the high-revving S65B40 naturally aspirated V8. This 4.0-liter power plant utilizes individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing to achieve a staggering 8,400 RPM redline. The chassis dynamics are anchored by a variable M differential lock and a subframe in excellent structural health. This example has undergone critical preventative maintenance, including rod bearing replacement and updated throttle actuators, ensuring the longevity of the high-tension internals. The 7-speed M-DCT gearbox delivers crisp, rev-matched downshifts, while the hydraulic steering rack provides the tactile feedback sought by purists. A robust, enthusiast-maintained driver that balances raw performance with mechanical reliability.",
